{"tid":2320581,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"Marvel Studio本日公布的電影新作情報(蟻俠最精彩：征服者康)","createTime":"2020-12-11T02:31:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-12T03:08:14.000Z","uid":105567,"like":17,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"7617370a193bdfe033ac79c362e3493c478c9071","tid":2320581,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T02:31:13.000Z","msg":"《Ant-Man and the Wasp: Quantumania》<br />\n本片為《蟻人》系列第三作，包括導演佩頓．李德（Peyton Reed）在內的老班底都將再次回歸。如同先前外界曾報導過的，喬納森．梅哲斯（Jonathan Majors）將在本片扮演「征服者」康恩（Kang the Conqueror）一角，凱瑟琳．紐頓（Kathryn Newton）則會扮演凱西．朗恩（Cassie Lang）。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/marvelstudios/posts/1116256305468647\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fmarvelstudios%2Fposts%2F1116256305468647&d=%2B91LnCbTcEAXcT2WrppvqXwIqWfEp03u%2FOlStsvMnxY%3D&h=c879d662\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/marvelstudios/posts/1116256305468647</a><br />\n<br />\n《Thor: Love and Thunder》 <br />\n《雷神索爾》系列第四集。克里斯汀．貝爾（Christian Bale）確定參演本片，並飾演「屠神者」果爾（Gorr the God Butcher）。本片將於2022年5月6日上映。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/marvelstudios/posts/1116253148802296\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fmarvelstudios%2Fposts%2F1116253148802296&d=%2B91LnCbTcEAXcT2WrppvqXwIqWfEp03u%2FOlStsvMnxY%3D&h=bb3ff083\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/marvelstudios/posts/1116253148802296</a><br />\n<br />\n《Captain Marvel 2》<br />\n《驚奇隊長》續集。本片導演為妮亞．達科斯塔（Nia DaCosta）。除了女主角布麗．拉森（Brie Larson）外，泰歐娜．帕利斯（Teyonah Parris）在影集《WandaVision》中飾演的成年版莫妮卡．藍博（Monica Rambeau）、伊曼．范拉尼（Iman Vellani）飾演的驚奇女士（Ms. Marvel）都將登場。本片將於2022年11月11日上映。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/marvelstudios/posts/1116235882137356\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fmarvelstudios%2Fposts%2F1116235882137356&d=%2B91LnCbTcEAXcT2WrppvqXwIqWfEp03u%2FOlStsvMnxY%3D&h=6dc6dfa9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/marvelstudios/posts/1116235882137356</a><br />\n<br />\n《Fantastic Four》<br />\n新版驚奇四超人電影，導演為曾經執導過《蜘蛛人：返校日》系列的強．華茲（Jon Watts）。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/marvelstudios/posts/1116263145467963\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fmarvelstudios%2Fposts%2F1116263145467963&d=%2B91LnCbTcEAXcT2WrppvqXwIqWfEp03u%2FOlStsvMnxY%3D&h=cf1dca38\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/marvelstudios/posts/1116263145467963</a><br />\n<br />\n影集部分<br />\n《I am Groot》<br />\n以小格魯特（Baby Groot）為主角的短片系列，本劇將會有其他不同尋常的角色登場。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/marvelstudios/posts/1116251825469095\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fmarvelstudios%2Fposts%2F1116251825469095&d=%2B91LnCbTcEAXcT2WrppvqXwIqWfEp03u%2FOlStsvMnxY%3D&h=4e0e15c3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/marvelstudios/posts/1116251825469095</a><br />\n<br />\n《The Guardians of the Galaxy Holiday Special》<br />\n標題令人聯想到《星際大戰》著名黑歷史的《星際異攻隊》節日特輯，詹姆斯．岡恩（James Gunn）將親自負責導演與編劇。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/marvelstudios/posts/1116250775469200\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fmarvelstudios%2Fposts%2F1116250775469200&d=%2B91LnCbTcEAXcT2WrppvqXwIqWfEp03u%2FOlStsvMnxY%3D&h=0f3251c3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/marvelstudios/posts/1116250775469200</a><br />\n<br />\n《Armor Wars》<br />\n唐．奇鐸（Don Cheadle）飾演的戰爭機器（War Machine）再次回歸。本作改編自漫畫裡的經典故事：假若東尼．史塔克（Tony Stark）的科技流入惡人之手，將會發生什麼事情？<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/marvelstudios/posts/1116248545469423\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fmarvelstudios%2Fposts%2F1116248545469423&d=%2B91LnCbTcEAXcT2WrppvqXwIqWfEp03u%2FOlStsvMnxY%3D&h=02a0d3a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/marvelstudios/posts/1116248545469423</a><br />\n<br />\n《Ironheart》<br />\n多明妮珂．索那（Dominique Thorne）將飾演主角芮芮．威廉斯（Riri Williams），她將會在劇中打造世上繼鋼鐵人（Iron Man）之後最先進的裝甲。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/marvelstudios/posts/1116246948802916\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fmarvelstudios%2Fposts%2F1116246948802916&d=%2B91LnCbTcEAXcT2WrppvqXwIqWfEp03u%2FOlStsvMnxY%3D&h=35511aeb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/marvelstudios/posts/1116246948802916</a><br />\n<br />\n《Secret Invasion》<br />\n山繆．傑克森（Samuel L. Jackson）將以尼克．福瑞（Nick Fury）的身分再度回歸。班．曼德森（Ben Mendelsohn）也會再次飾演塔洛斯（Talos）一角。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/marvelstudios/posts/1116245485469729\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fmarvelstudios%2Fposts%2F1116245485469729&d=%2B91LnCbTcEAXcT2WrppvqXwIqWfEp03u%2FOlStsvMnxY%3D&h=e0e3b66e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/marvelstudios/posts/1116245485469729</a>"},{"pid":"38ebfdbb8658e89f2734c0106cc574f4d9e62a4f","tid":2320581,"uid":160592,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T02:38:05.000Z","msg":"Kathryn Newton<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e837a6631f8ea9a3695c77785b62bfb98b9b7e3","tid":2320581,"uid":93986,"like":9,"dislike":3,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T02:42:57.000Z","msg":"黑人黑人黑人黑人"},{"pid":"82564146e6456203cf35c88965f8f8b0dbcc90c7","tid":2320581,"uid":58630,"like":10,"dislike":3,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T02:46:54.000Z","msg":"Marvel出變性人角色未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ab137811de157b8b0d5dccbf914c72af9a5a5e3","tid":2320581,"uid":52215,"like":10,"dislike":11,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T02:48:32.000Z","msg":"仲Marvel <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Out哂啦"},{"pid":"6c08a319c94bc123c9c938dec4428a68773b10a3","tid":2320581,"uid":295602,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T02:50:51.000Z","msg":"Cap